KEY TERMS
In this Privacy Policy, (i) capitalised terms defined by inclusion in quotations and/or parenthesis have the meanings so ascribed; and (ii) the following terms have the meanings assigned to them herein below. Terms not defined in this Privacy Policy shall have the same meaning as assigned in the Terms and Conditions published on the Website.
1.1       “
Consent
” means any freely given, specific, informed, and unambiguous indication of the Data Subject’s wishes by which they, by a statement or by a clear affirmative action, signify agreement to the Processing of Personal Data relating to them;
1.2       “
